<h1>Your Text Analysis</h1>
<% t = @analyzed_text %>
<h2>Number of Words: <%= t.count_of_words %></h2>

<h2>Vowels: <%= t.count_of_vowels %></h2>

<h2>Consonants: <%= t.count_of_consonants %></h2>

<h2>Most Common Letter: <%= t.most_used_letter.keys[0].upcase %>, used <%= t.most_used_letter.values[0] %> times</h2>
